  50,37,"In that is a reminder for whoever possesses a heart, or cares to listen and witness"
  50,38,"We created the heavens and the earth and what is between them in six days, and no fatigue touched Us"
  50,39,"So endure what they say, and proclaim the praises of your Lord before the rising of the sun, and before sunset"
  50,40,"And glorify Him during the night, and at the end of devotions"
  50,41,And listen for the Day when the caller calls from a nearby place
  50,42,The Day when they will hear the Shout in all truth. That is the Day of Emergence
  50,43,"It is We who control life and death, and to Us is the destination"
  50,44,The Day when the earth will crack for them at once. That is an easy gathering for Us
  50,45,"We are fully aware of what they say, and you are not a dictator over them. So remind by the Quran whoever fears My warning"
